Package: vdiffr
Title: Visual Regression Testing and Graphical Diffing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lionel", "Henry", , "lionel@rstudio.com", c("cre", "aut")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph"))
Description: An extension to testthat that makes it easy to add
    graphical unit tests. It provides a Shiny application to manage
    the test cases.
